casebody.data:
Lang, Appellant, et al. v. Hanlon et al. (No. 8,

March T., 1931.)

November 23, 1931:

Opinión by

Mr. Justice Maxey,

This is an appeal of Elizabeth Lang from the judgment of the court below entering judgment n. o. v. in *386favor of the defendant, M. A. Hanlon. The judgment is affirmed for the reasons set forth in the opinion filed to No. 182, March Term, 1931.
